5. If any test FAILS:
   - Fix it immediately
   - Re-run only that test
   - Update TEST-REPORT.md with PASSED
   - Never deploy if critical tests fail

6. Critical tests that must NEVER fail:
   - Form submits to database
   - Homepage loads
   - API endpoints respond
   - Admin dashboard loads
   - Mobile layout works

7. After all tests pass update TEST-REPORT.md
   with final PASSED status and live URL